# CSViewer-TUI (cvit)

CSV Viewer in TUI using Textual and textual-fastdatatable.
It can also be used in the Linux console.

## Usage
### using uv
```bash
curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh
```
```bash
uv tool install csviewer-tui
```
```bash
cvit example.csv
```
